\">Maria Barbieri\u003C/a>\u003C/p>  \u003Cp> Il 16 Agosto Feridius servo della dea Cerere si unì carnalmente con tre adolescenti dei quali i nomi erano per legge Onesimus, L. Valerius Cassianus e Filumenus. Il solo Taurus (giacque) con quella donna, augurio ----.\u003C/p>  ",{"id":217,"html":218},"commentary","\u003Ch2>commentary\u003C/h2>  \u003Cp>A substantial text incised in the wall of room of a Roman house (late Republican / early Empire according to Orsi), but in a phase of dereliction after the original use of the house in Orsi's view. The text is incised within an outline of a tabula ansata. In large letters below the main text is the word PROPITIAM. Several other graffiti are recorded in the same room.\u003C/p>  ",{"id":220,"html":221},"bibliography","\u003Ch2>bibliography\u003C/h2>  \u003Cul>\u003Cli> 1919.0057 \u003Ca href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001283\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001283\u003C/a>\u003C/li>\u003Cli> Orsi NSA 1918 58-60 fig.7 \u003Ca href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001392\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001392\u003C/a>\u003C/li>\u003Cli> Manganaro 1962 490-491 \u003Ca href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001851\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001851\u003C/a>\u003C/li>\u003Cli> Manganaro 1988 68 n.348 \u003Ca href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001427\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001427\u003C/a>\u003C/li>\u003C/ul>  \u003Cul>\u003Cli>\u003C/li>\u003C/ul>  ",{"id":223,"html":224},"handnote"," Line 1    Interlineation line 1 to 2    ",{"id":226,"html":227},"license"," Licensed under a Creative Commons-Attribution 4.0 licence. ",[229,231,234,235],{"html":230},"Text encoding: Maria Barbieri",{"id":232,"lang":102,"html":233},"edition-interpretive","\u003Cdiv class=\"textpart\" lang=\"la\">\u003Cspan class=\"ab\" id=\"div-interpretive\">  \u003Ca id=\"al1-interpretive\">\u003C!--0-->\